  "texts": [
    "In addition to the traditional P2D model 105, a hybrid neural network model CNN-SAM-LSTM 106 has been recently employed to estimate full battery lifetime, including SOH and SOC.",
    "107 employed transfer learning to predict the capacity (SOC) based on the voltage relaxation.",
    "Severson et al.",
    "108 utilized the data-driven prediction of the battery cycle (SOH) before the battery degraded.",
    "Recently, Ge et al."
  ]
